languages.text: "Стой, Эклендиль! Ты не вернешь наш дом, пролив невинную кровь. Элантах повин{mf|ен|на} лишь в том, что помог{mf||ла} мне добраться сюда и сбросить твои оковы".

traits.locale_text: "Стой! Элантах невинов{mf|ен|на}, теперь я знаю это наверняка! {mf|Он|Она} помогал{mf||а} мне все это время. Прошу. Не нужно этого делать".
traits.speaker: YrlietCompanion

languages.text: "Wait, Eklendyl! Shedding innocent blood will not bring our home back. The elantach is guilty only of helping me to reach this place and free you."
languages.original_text: "Стой, Эклендиль! Ты не вернешь наш дом, пролив невинную кровь. Элантах повин{mf|ен|на} лишь в том, что помог{mf||ла} мне добраться сюда и сбросить твои оковы".

traits.locale_text: "Wait, Eklendyl! Shedding innocent blood will not bring our home back. The elantach is guilty only of helping me to reach this place and free you."
traits.speaker: YrlietCompanion

traits.locale_text: "Wait! The elantach is not guilty. I am certain of it now! {mf|H|Sh}e has been helping me all this time. Please. There is no need to do this."
traits.speaker: YrlietCompanion

traits.locale_text: "Wait, Eklendyl! Shedding innocent blood will not bring our home back. The elantach is guilty only of helping me to reach this place and free you."

traits.locale_text: "Wait, Eklendyl! Shedding innocent blood will not bring our home back. The elantach is guilty only of helping me to reach this place and free you."
traits.speaker: YrlietCompanion

languages.text: «¡Espera, Eklendyl! Derramar sangre inocente no nos devolverá nuestro hogar. Lo único que ha hecho {mf|el|la} elantach es ayudarme a llegar aquí y a liberarte».
languages.original_text: "Wait, Eklendyl! Shedding innocent blood will not bring our home back. The elantach is guilty only of helping me to reach this place and free you."

traits.locale_text: «¡Espera! {mf|El|La} elantach no es culpable. ¡Ahora lo sé! Todo este tiempo no ha hecho otra cosa que ayudarme. Por favor. Esto no es necesario».
traits.speaker: YrlietCompanion

languages.text: 「待て、エクレンディル！罪なき者の血をいくら流がそうとも、我らの故郷は帰ってはこない。そのエランタの罪は、我をここに送り届け、お前を解放する手助けをしたことだけだ」
languages.original_text: "Wait, Eklendyl! Shedding innocent blood will not bring our home back. The elantach is guilty only of helping me to reach this place and free you."

traits.locale_text: 「待て、エクレンディル！罪なき者の血をいくら流がそうとも、我らの故郷は帰ってはこない。そのエランタの罪は、我をここに送り届け、お前を解放する手助けをしたことだけだ」
traits.speaker: YrlietCompanion

languages.text: “等等，埃克伦迪！就算洒下无辜者的鲜血，也无法换回我们的家园。外界人没有任何罪过，是他帮助我来到了这个地方，救出了你。”
languages.original_text: "Wait, Eklendyl! Shedding innocent blood will not bring our home back. The elantach is guilty only of helping me to reach this place and free you."

traits.locale_text: “等等！外界人没有罪过，我现在非常肯定！这么长时间以来，{mf|他|她}一直都在帮助我。我恳求你，没有必要这么做。”
traits.speaker: YrlietCompanion

languages.text: « Attendez, Eklendyl ! Verser le sang d'{mf|un innocent|une innocente} ne nous rendra pas notre monde. L'elantach n'a rien à se reprocher, {mf|il|elle} n'a fait que m'aider à venir jusqu'ici pour vous libérer. »
languages.original_text: "Wait, Eklendyl! Shedding innocent blood will not bring our home back. The elantach is guilty only of helping me to reach this place and free you."

traits.locale_text: « Attendez ! L'elantach n'a rien à se reprocher. J'en suis désormais certaine ! Tout ce temps, {mf|il|elle} n'a fait que m'aider. Je vous en prie. Tout ceci est inutile. »
traits.speaker: YrlietCompanion

languages.text: "Wartet, Eklendyl! Unschuldiges Blut zu vergießen, bringt uns unsere Heimat nicht zurück. Der Elantach ist nur schuldig, mir geholfen zu haben, hierher zu gelangen und Euch zu befreien."
languages.original_text: "Wait, Eklendyl! Shedding innocent blood will not bring our home back. The elantach is guilty only of helping me to reach this place and free you."

traits.locale_text: "Wartet! {mf|Der|Die} Elantach hat recht. Da bin ich mir jetzt sicher! {mf|Er|Sie} hat mir die ganze Zeit geholfen. Bitte. Es ist nicht nötig, das zu tun."
traits.speaker: YrlietCompanion

languages.text: "Eklendyl, dur! Masum kanı dökmek, bize yuvamızı geri vermeyecek. Elantach'ın tek kabahati, buraya gelip seni serbest bırakmama yardımcı olmak."
languages.original_text: "Wait, Eklendyl! Shedding innocent blood will not bring our home back. The elantach is guilty only of helping me to reach this place and free you."
